1
00:00:04,100 --> 00:00:09,280
♪Looking up at the burning future♪

2
00:00:10,950 --> 00:00:16,040
♪We are like the ever-lasting dust♪

3
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:21,000
♪Even if we drift
in the dazzling mundane world♪

4
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:23,070
♪We will not bloom♪

5
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:28,610
♪As long as my life still exists♪

6
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:33,520
♪The colors in my heart
will never fade away♪

7
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,280
♪The crowd drowns me♪

8
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,110
♪Time burns me♪

9
00:00:37,110 --> 00:00:40,320
♪Amid the ashes, stars still twinkle♪

10
00:00:40,430 --> 00:00:42,410
♪Even if I stand alone♪

11
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:47,180
♪I'll still remember
to clench my fists tightly♪

12
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:50,620
=Behind The Scenes=

13
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:54,940
=Episode 4=
=A Forced Confinement=

14
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:47,510
Sorry, Miss Bai.

15
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:52,870
My life can't be given to you for now.

16
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,520
She still doesn't say anything.

17
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,750
Continue?

18
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:32,310
Miss Bai,

19
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,800
I don't know what happened

20
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,710
that caused such a big misunderstanding,

21
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,430
you even tried every means to kill me.

22
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,750
But I can responsibly tell you

23
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,240
that many things are not

24
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:47,400
as they seem.

25
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:49,550
I think we can

26
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,150
communicate in a more civilized manner.

27
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,750
What do you think?

28
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,030
Mr. Yan,

29
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,430
stop pretending to be so innocent.

30
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:03,190
I don't know how you got my father's badge.

31
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:05,150
But I know

32
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,470
his death

33
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,800
is related to you.

34
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,190
This is the reason I want to kill you.

35
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,310
As long as I am alive for a day,

36
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,960
I will not give up on killing you.

37
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:21,870
Unless

38
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,240
you kill me first.

39
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,080
I see.

40
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:32,560
It seems before it is resolved,

41
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,630
you plan to be with me for a lifetime.

42
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,800
With a beauty like you by my side,

43
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:47,190
I will certainly accompany you.

44
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,280
Interesting.

45
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,190
You make me more and more fascinated.

46
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,030
I'll take care of the rest.

47
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,400
You all go back first.

48
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,520
But...

49
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:40,830
Is she still not willing to eat?

50
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,310
It's been three days already.

51
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,240
If this continues,

52
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,630
I'm afraid something might happen.

53
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,000
Why don't you eat?

54
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,160
Why don't you kill me?

55
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,190
It seems like you've misunderstood me.

56
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,510
Murder is against the law.

57
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:16,950
If you want to avenge your father,

58
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,360
then you can't take it so lightly.

59
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,390
Just give up after one failure?

60
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,190
If you starve yourself to death,

61
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,240
you will only see

62
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,750
the murderer living freely outside.

63
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,310
You don't have the right to mention him.

64
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,870
You are unworthy.

65
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,070
One day

66
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,720
I will kill you with my own hands.

67
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,310
Just eat.

68
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,760
Then you have the strength to kill me.

69
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:51,300
♪The memories slip away between fingers♪

70
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,320
Let me go.

71
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:53,920
Kill me.

72
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:57,360
Let me go.

73
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,070
One day I will kill you with my own hands.

74
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,600
Want to kill me?

75
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,310
First eat your fill.

76
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:09,220
Eat.

77
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:15,810
♪Dreams are clouds that will bloom♪

78
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:18,440
♪Every time the sunlight shines down♪

79
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:21,040
I will definitely kill you with my own hands.

80
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:25,640
♪In the depths of time♪

81
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,280
♪It warms me deeply♪

82
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,000
Mr. Cheng,

83
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:47,040
this is Mr. Yan's private territory.

84
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,830
You brought people here without permission.

85
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,080
What does it mean?

86
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:54,420
(Search Warrant)

87
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,800
You are suspected of detaining others.

88
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:00,180
Please cooperate with our investigation.

89
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,750
We will naturally cooperate.

90
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,270
But you better find something.

91
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:07,480
Otherwise, I suspect the Patrol Station

92
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,480
is targeting us.

93
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,400
Where's Yan Liang?

94
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,720
Didn't anyone tell you?

95
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:17,120
The president went to report the case.

96
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,560
What?

97
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,310
Good for you, Yan Liang.

98
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:29,240
I didn't expect you to come here on your own.

99
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:32,510
Mr. Cheng,

100
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,310
I'm here to report a case.

101
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:35,480
I'm not turning myself in.

102
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,870
No need for that, right?

103
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,000
Where did you hide White Peony?

104
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,310
Didn't you already search my house?

105
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:51,030
What?

106
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:52,270
Didn’t find her?

107
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,510
I advise you not to play tricks.

108
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:54,950
Even if there is no evidence,

109
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:57,390
I also have the right to arrest you.

110
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,080
Report.

111
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:05,560
Miss Bai just appeared in Grand World.

112
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,800
I said that it was a misunderstanding.

113
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,630
I am a law-abiding good citizen.

114
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,510
Why do you always want to wrong me?

115
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,000
What do you want to do?

116
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:18,310
I said I'm here to report a case.

117
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,000
What case?

118
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:30,310
80 million in the bank was stolen.

119
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:36,980
=Behind The Scenes=

120
