♪The world is heartless♪

121
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,680
♪Why should we shed tears for love?♪

122
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:02,620
♪The fading rain in the spring smoke♪

123
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:06,600
♪Where can I seek the broken soul?♪

124
00:09:07,370 --> 00:09:10,160
♪Even the cold pillow is heartless♪

125
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:13,570
♪You don’t know my heart♪

126
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:17,650
♪Dreams shattered, with no one to speak♪

127
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:21,370
♪I fear the most that you leave me♪

128
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,640
♪With what kind of gaze♪

129
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,400
♪What kind of identity♪

130
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,670
♪Should I wait
for your glance and a kiss?♪

131
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,870
♪No matter how far♪

132
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:32,810
♪No matter how many lifetimes♪

133
00:09:32,810 --> 00:09:35,650
♪I long to see your love, no parting♪

134
00:09:35,650 --> 00:09:38,330
♪I just want to be with you♪

135
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:42,490
♪Roaming the mortal world together♪

136
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:46,050
♪Even if I have to go♪

137
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:49,750
♪Through several reincarnations♪

138
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:53,480
♪I just want to be with you♪

139
00:09:53,890 --> 00:09:58,300
♪Under the falling stars♪

140
